    "description": {
      "zh": "Badger Ordnance 集成导轨框架适配所有Accuracy International Chassis 2.0枪托系统（AS50型号除外），可替换现有两脚架安装模块，支持加装A/N PVS-22、A/N PVS-24、A/N PVS-27等夹式夜视装置及热成像仪/融合观测仪等战术附件。",
      "en": "The Badger Ordnance IMUNS installs into any Accuracy International Chassis 2.0 (except AS 50’s), replaces the current bipod mounting block and allows the use of clip on night vision devices such as the A/N PVS-22, A/N PVS-24, A/N PVS-27 or other devices like thermal imagers or fusion devices."
